{
  "texts": [
    "The latency is reported using StreamLAAL (Papi et al., 2024).",
    "For the en→de language direction, the latency and BLEU scores are reported at the word level using the 13a tokenizer.",
    "Alternatively, for the en→zh language direction, the latency and BLEU scores are reported at the character level.",
    "Our fine-tuning and evaluation for the Gemma 12B models was conducted on an NVIDIA H200.",
    "Alternatively, the Gemma 4B models were trained on a NVIDIA A40 and evaluated on a NVIDIA V100."
  ]
}